{"tid":2433908,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲SBS停播中共央視與CGTN新聞節目","createTime":"2021-03-05T07:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T07:46:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49001fdf6a9b50a753722dd1bd91d7fcaf15aa37","tid":2433908,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"澳洲公共廣播機構SBS遭人權組織施壓後，決定暫停轉播中國央視（CCTV）和轄下中國環球電視網（CGTN）的新聞節目，包括15分鐘的普通話新聞和30分鐘的英語新聞。 人權組織「保護衛士」（Safeguard Defenders）早前發電郵至SBS，批評CCTV在2013年至2020年，播出約56人次承認控罪的片段，指稱這些人是受到脅逼而作出虛假供詞。SBS表示，已接獲投訴並正檢討，決定暫時停播相關節目，會重新評估相關服務。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/f50df34b89438a3a698c948586d62a0d/2021/03/1aadce6104d6100d5a59fb98b03a72df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2Ff50df34b89438a3a698c948586d62a0d%2F2021%2F03%2F1aadce6104d6100d5a59fb98b03a72df.jpg&h=121c92c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2381708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2381708&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUpAcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=acaac99b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2381708</a>"},{"pid":"b0d321fccad1fec24349a26f357a72f6aefa229f","tid":2433908,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"但法國政府好似批咗牌？"},{"pid":"df64b9dd9d40912077681a8271a357a48b56efcc","tid":2433908,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0d321fccad1fec24349a26f357a72f6aefa229f","tid":2433908,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"但法國政府好似批咗牌？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"法國批係歐洲 而家講緊澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}